2
00:01:48,267 --> 00:01:51,930
"and so shall be saved
from mine enemies!"

3
00:01:52,871 --> 00:01:56,273
"The waves of death
have closed about me!

4
00:01:57,843 --> 00:02:01,541
"The cords of hell
have encompassed me about,

5
00:02:02,381 --> 00:02:05,817
"and the snares of death
